  <rte>
    <name>Colwith Force and Skelwith Force from Elterwater</name>
	<desc>This circular Lake District walk explores part of the Langdale and Elterwater area of Lakeland. While no tops are included, two waterfalls provide picturesque landmarks, Colwith Force and Skelwith Force. </desc>
	<author>Copyright Walking Britain</author>
	<url>www.walkingbritain.co.uk/walk-1059-description</url>
